body.raw:
# Batteries


## Electrical

- Cell Voltage
- Capacity Test
- Discharge Test


## Maintenance

- Electrolyte Level
- Terminal Tight.
- Cleaning

4. Ins. Resist.
5. Sat. Curve

# Motors


## Electrical

2. Tight. Check

## Activities

1. Ins. Resist.
2. Wind. Resist.
3. Turns Ratio
4. Mag. Current
5. Dielec. Absorp.
6. Diss. Gas Analysis
7. Sweep Freq. Resp.

document.title: Circuit Breaker
document.description: Maintenance activities for Circuit Breaker in HV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Circuit Breaker

## Activities

1. Contact Resist.
2. Timing Open-Close
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Coil Pickup
5. SF6 Gas Press.-Purity
6. Vacuum Integrity
7. Mech. Operation

## Activities

1. Pickup-Dropout
2. Contact Resist.
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Mech. Endurance

document.title: Differential
document.description: Maintenance activities for Differential in HV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Differential

## Activities

1. Rat/Ph Angle
2. Slope Char.
3. Harm. Restr.
4. Ins. Resist.
5. Functional

## Mechanical

- Contact Align.
- Operation Test


## Safety

- Interlock Check
- Position Indication


## Electrical

- Ins. Resist.
- Contact Resistance

## Activities

1. Trip Time SC-OL
2. Ins. Resist.

document.description: Maintenance activities for Overcurrent in HV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Overcurrent

## Activities

1. Pickup
2. Timing
3. Char. Curve
4. Ins. Resist.
5. Burden

## Activities

1. Volt. Matching
2. Phase Angle
3. Freq. Matching

- Dielectric Test

document.title: Distribution Board
document.description: Maintenance activities for Distribution Board in LV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Distribution Board


## Insulation

- Ins. Resist.
- Phase-Phase Test
- Phase-Earth Test


## Busbar

- Busbar Tightness
- Connection Test
- Thermal Scan


## Voltage

- Volt. Stability
- Voltage Drop


## Verification

- Phase Seq. Verif.
- Labeling Check


## Protection

- Func. Breaker-RCD Coord.
- RCD Test Button
- Earth Connection

document.description: Maintenance activities for UPS in LV SWGR system

body.raw:
# UPS


## Battery

- Battery Cal.
- Battery Volt.
- Cell Measurement


## Performance

- Backup Time
- Efficiency
- Load Test


## System

- Alarms
- Controls
- Display Test

document.description: Maintenance activities for Contactor in MV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Contactor

## Activities

1. Pickup-Dropout
2. Contact Resist.
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Mech. Endurance

# Directional OC

## Activities

1. Discrimination
2. Pickup
3. Timing

## Activities

1. Pickup
2. Timing
3. Ins. Resist.

## Activities

1. Func. Trip-Reset
2. Contact Resist.
3. Coil Pickup

document.description: Maintenance activities for Motor Prot. in MV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Motor Prot.

## Activities

1. Starting Time
2. Stall Prot.
3. Thermal OL
4. Unbal./Ph Loss

## Activities

1. Relay Settings
2. Trip Test
3. Communication Check
4. Indicator Test

## Activities

2. Phase Angle

body.raw:
# Main Unit

## Activities

1. Insulation Resistance
2. Timing Open-Close
3. Contact Resistance
4. Gas Pressure
5. Functional Interlock

2. Timing

## Activities

1. Visual Insp.
2. Tight. Check
3. Polarity Verif.

## Activities

1. Moist. Content
2. Dielec. Strength
3. Acidity

- Operation Count


## Control

- Remote Operation

# Starting Time

This is the documentation page for **Starting Time** which is part of the **Motor Prot.** subcategory in the **Relay** section.

## Overview

Add a brief overview of Starting Time here.

## Procedure

3. Step three of the Starting Time procedure

| Parameter 2 | Description of parameter 2 | Default value |

## Notes

Additional notes about Starting Time can be added here.

# Thermal OL

This is the documentation page for **Thermal OL** which is part of the **Motor Prot.** subcategory in the **Relay** section.

## Overview

Add a brief overview of Thermal OL here.

## Procedure

1. Step one of the Thermal OL procedure
2. Step two of the Thermal OL procedure
3. Step three of the Thermal OL procedure

## Parameters

| Parameter | Description | Default Value |
|-----------|-------------|---------------|
| Parameter 1 | Description of parameter 1 | Default value |
| Parameter 2 | Description of parameter 2 | Default value |

## Notes

Additional notes about Thermal OL can be added here.

## Related Activities

- Other related activities from Motor Prot.

This is the documentation page for **CT Polarity** which is part of the **Trafo Diff.** subcategory in the **Relay** section.

## Overview

# Inrush Restraint

This is the documentation page for **Inrush Restraint** which is part of the **Trafo Diff.** subcategory in the **Relay** section.

## Overview

Add a brief overview of Inrush Restraint here.

# Timing

This is the documentation page for **Timing** which is part of the **Underfreq.** subcategory in the **Relay** section.

## Overview

## Procedure

# Timing

This is the documentation page for **Timing** which is part of the **Undervolt.** subcategory in the **Relay** section.

## Overview

Add a brief overview of Timing here.

## Procedure

1. Step one of the Timing procedure
2. Step two of the Timing procedure
3. Step three of the Timing procedure

## Parameters

| Parameter | Description | Default Value |
|-----------|-------------|---------------|
| Parameter 1 | Description of parameter 1 | Default value |
| Parameter 2 | Description of parameter 2 | Default value |

## Notes

Additional notes about Timing can be added here.
